Xd_dtt_progression :

This an space-abstract themed map where you need to pass 27 traps . You can pass each traps with several way . This is the second XD (xtrem-death) maps by the Developing-Trust-Team . 

Special tanks to Tixi from my team for the "Dogers" in displacement !

Note : If you are running this maps on a serveur Tick-Rate 100 put this line command : phys_timescale 1 and mp_flashlight 1 if you want to use the flashlight ! You can add a bot to do't restart the round when you die and respawn in return to CTs-Team to respawn !

http://teamdtt.o-n.fr

Enjoy !
